title: MAYC purchase (28/10/2021) for MC DAO
body:
The result of the first vote was to buy 20-30 MAYC (floor):

https://snapshot.org/#/mutantsdao.eth/proposal/0xc97c0c69e3f9a9a4b75ecf4a61581fcbf516f18c1038ef7e764b628ef7249cfe

Please vote on the quantity! Also some further options not in the previous vote are also being included:
- Non-floor MAYC (for example, M2 only instead of M1)
- Other quantity of Floor MAYC
- NONE
